{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":10,"day":21}],"page_start":2,"page_end":2,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"毛主席；我们永远跟着您！","authors":["文儒"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"身上为什么这样热？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里为什么这样暖？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为我们是站在敬爱的领袖毛主席身边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士都有一个最美好的心愿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是被敬爱的领袖毛主席接见。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天天盼呵夜夜盼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于盼到了这最幸福的一天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《东方红》的乐曲刚刚奏起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席来到了我们面前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万颗火热的心呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拨动着一个共同的心弦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“毛主席万岁，万万岁！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"代表着我们心中的万语千言。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席呵毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您是我们心中的红太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您的书是我们的最高指示，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您的话是我们的行动指南。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您的思想武装了我们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使我们最坚强最勇敢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席呵毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们永远跟着您，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一辈子为人民服务，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一辈子当革命闯将！"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}